                <h1>How HireRight Conducts Employment Verification</h1>
                <p>Hireright verifies employment by reaching out to previous employers to confirm candidates' job titles, dates of employment, and responsibilities. This process may include background checks, reviewing employment records, and communicating with HR departments. Their goal is to ensure accurate representations in job applications.</p>
